          "id": "medmcqa-30580d2d-7ee8-4125-8fc0-33dbb18e0438",
          "text": "Child presents with linear verrucous plaques on the trunk with vacuolation of keratinocytes in S.Spinosum and S.Granulosum. Diagnosis is?",
