          "explanation": "Ans. is 'a' Dapsone The drug of choice for Dermatitis herpetiformis - Dapsone (50-200 mg/day)Dermatitis herpetiformis is a bullous lesion in which there is Gluten Hypersensitivity. Treatment -Dapsone*Gluten free diet*Vitamins & minerals",
