          "text": "A mother brought her child who has got a vascular plaque like lesion over the lateral aspect of forehead mainly involving ophthalmic and maxillary division of trigeminal nerve. Mother says that the lesion has remained unchanged since bih. Also mother gives a history that the child is on valproate for seizure disorder. What is the MOST probable diagnosis ?",
