          "id": "medmcqa-57c35284-4271-4a28-ba94-8ef8ce2dae1f",
          "text": "A patient with psoriasis was started on systemic steroids. After stopping the treatment, the patient developed generalized pustules all over the body. The cause is most likely to be:",
