          "id": "medmcqa-5583ec1f-bf80-4764-96dc-2183ec6649b3",
          "text": "Patient with pruritic lesion over Left shoulder showing cigarette paper atrophy and poikiloderma with generalized lymphadenopathy. Histopathologv exmanination of lesion shows CD4 positive sezary leutzner cells. What is the dermo- epidermal manifestation of this disease?",
