          "id": "medmcqa-5cb5adf1-ac54-4390-9768-40ee00845635",
          "text": "A 24 year old unmarried woman has multiple nodular, cystic, pustular and comadonic lesions on face, upper back and shoulders for 2 years. The drug of choice for her treatment.",
