          "id": "medmcqa-8d75a9b6-6c52-4d9d-9364-414c18b5c8d3",
          "text": "A 70 year old farmer ,presented to you with complaints of yellowish discolouration of his finger nails for the past 6 months, he also gives history of recurrent episodes of itiching in the groin for which he used to take local home made herbal remedy. On examination 3 of his toe nails also show similar change with tunneling. Which among the following is the best test for rapid confirmation of your diagnosis?",
