          "id": "medmcqa-ecb4c0c4-e628-4d23-90d3-16d51b51419f",
          "text": "A 30 year old male patient has a large, spreading and exuberant ulcer with bright red granulation tissue over the glans penis. There was no lymphadenopathy. The most likely causative organism is;",
