          "text": "A 30 year old male presented with itchy, papulovesicular lesions in the extensor aspect of elbows and knees. Biopsy of the lesion showed dermoepidermal blister with micro-abscesses. Immunofluorescence showed deposits of IgA in the tips of dermal papillae. What is the MOST likely diagnosis?",
