          "explanation": "Ans. a. Pemphigus vulgarisMucosal involvement, nikolsky sign (exfoliation of skin on rubbing) positive, flaccid bulla with erosions - all are features of pemphigus vulgaris.Target lesions are seen in erythema multiformeMucosal involvement is absent in bullous pemphogoid.",
