          "id": "medmcqa-fc8b7331-5c36-44a1-a5e0-3395fe4be955",
          "text": "A 12 year old boy had a gradually progressive plaque on a buttock for the last 3 years. The plaque was 15 cm in diameter, annular in shape, with crusting and induration at the periphery and scarring at the center. The most likely diagnosis.",
