          "id": "medmcqa-1c9a91d0-2a4c-4cb3-9481-28f9f15a72f8",
          "text": "A caretaker in a nursing home presents with pruritus of her trunk and extremities. On physical examination, she has several erythematous papules in her finger webs, axillae, umbilicus, and groin areas. Her scalp is clear. Which of the following is the best treatment for this woman?",
