          "id": "medmcqa-8fefb687-ac1b-4406-ae84-45bb675a157f",
          "text": "Extremely pruritic excoriation and papules on buttocks with autoantibodies against epidermal transglutaminase and IgA deposition in dermis on immunohistological examination of normal perilesional skin. Diagnosis is?",
